    <title><![CDATA[博客搭建记录]]></title>
    <link href="http://elecsliu.com/2014/11/01/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/"/>
    <id>http://elecsliu.com/2014/11/01/博客搭建记录/</id>
    <published>2014-11-01T02:10:51.000Z</published>
    <updated>2014-11-01T08:00:13.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1.使用Pacman主题<br>2.添加多说评论<br>3.文章重复现象解决办法：删除博客根目录下的db.jason<br>4.在variable.styl文件中修改主题配色</p>
<figure class="highlight {bash}"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">color</span>-blue = <span class="preprocessor">#20b2aa ##修改标题颜色为浅海洋绿</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">color</span>-theme = <span class="preprocessor">#20b2aa ##修改主题基础颜色为浅海洋绿</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>5.按照Pacman主题说明文件夹和文件后，在每次写文章时使用如下语法即可：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">tags:</div><div class="line">- 标签名</div><div class="line">categories:</div><div class="line">- 目录名</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>6.将博客URL提交到搜索引擎:将搜索引擎的meta验证标签复制到 hexo\themes\pacman\layout_partial\head.ejs的head中<br>7.使用百度统计:<br>编辑文件 hexo\themes\pacman_config.yml, 增加配置项：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">baidu_tongji: <span class="literal">true</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>新建文件 hexo\themes\pacman\layout_partial\baidu_tongji.ejs, 内容如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;% <span class="keyword">if</span> (theme.baidu_tongji){ %&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;script <span class="built_in">type</span>=<span class="string">"text/javascript"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#我的百度统计代码</span></div><div class="line">&lt;/script&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;% } %&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>编辑文件 hexo\themes\modernist\layout_partial\head.ejs, 在<head>之前增加：</head></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;%- partial(<span class="string">'baidu_tongji'</span>) %&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>参考文章：<a href="http://www.tuicool.com/articles/AfQnQjy" target="_blank" rel="external">hexo你的博客</a><br>8.在<a href="http://www.pinpaibao.cn/" target="_blank" rel="external">品牌宝</a>申请个人网站认证</p>
]]></content>
